OL,3,CSexual offences trial of Jeffrey
OL,4,CDonaldson enters its third week
OL,6,FThe sexual offences trial of Sir
OL,7,FJeffrey Donaldson and his wife is
OL,8,Fentering its third week.
OL,10,FThe former leader of the DUP arrived
OL,11,Fat Newry Crown Court shortly after 9am
OL,12,Fon Monday.
OL,14,FThe ex-MP, 63, has pleaded not guilty
OL,15,Fto 18 alleged offences.
OL,17,FThe charges include one count of rape
OL,18,Fand allegations of indecent assault
OL,19,Fand gross indecency, and span a time
OL,20,Fperiod between 1985 and 2008 involving
OL,21,Ftwo alleged victims.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
