OL,3,CSexual offences trial of Jeffrey
OL,4,CDonaldson enters its third week
OL,6,FComplainant A and B have both
OL,7,Fpreviously given evidence at the
OL,8,Fsexual offences trial.
OL,10,FLady Donaldson denies several charges
OL,11,Fof aiding and abetting her husband's
OL,12,Falleged offending.
OL,14,FShe is facing a trial of the facts.
OL,16,FThe prosecution case will continue on
OL,17,FMonday when it is expected that the
OL,18,Fjury of seven men and five women will
OL,19,Fbe played police interviews with the
OL,20,FDonaldsons.
